{
  "stem": "12491.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Within a few hours after the Germans left, a motorcycle with a side wagon came up with the SS, and they wanted to speak to Mr.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Schindler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And our guards in the boots pointed their guns at them and said Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Schindler is gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You cannot come in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we can't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We need gas.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We gave them gas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Schindler left warehouses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We gave them gasoline.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they wanted plans of the factory, of what Schindler was doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we didn't give it to them and they just turned around and went away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes and no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was surprised that no one else except my friend and I were people from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other people were from who knows where.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never knew them then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know them now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never was in contact with them after I left Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess observation or whatever, behavior, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were Czechoslovakian people, specialists, working in the camp, coming and going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used them as-- what do you call them-- communication links.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were coming into the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they were not necessarily part of the underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe they were, maybe they were not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were just Czech people who came-- specialists in whatever we needed-- and they-- but there were several of them, five, seven, nine, whatever-- and they used to go home for the evening then come back in the morning.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a pass.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a pass.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody must have approached them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't I, and I wasn't even-- no, I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was done in pairs so, case somebody gets caught, he doesn't know who else there is is in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
